00:40:08,320 --> 00:40:10,640
What I want is not only the flourish of Peking University. 

1142
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:13,600
What I want is the flourish of China

1143
00:40:14,240 --> 00:40:16,240
We can't get by not talking, not arguing, not fighting.

1144
00:40:16,720 --> 00:40:18,240
What you said, what you want.

1145
00:40:18,400 --> 00:40:20,240
I can understand and I support it. 

1146
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:20,960
So.

1147
00:40:21,280 --> 00:40:21,840
May Fourth Movement

