I attended the demonstration in person.

1154
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:32,240
But it's different now.

1155
00:40:32,720 --> 00:40:34,960
Students don't attend classes, professors don't teach.

1156
00:40:35,440 --> 00:40:37,520
All schools in Beijing have gone on strike.

1157
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:39,520
Everyone has gone to politics.

1158
00:40:40,080 --> 00:40:42,080
The whole society is in chaos, brother Zhongfu.

1159
00:40:42,640 --> 00:40:43,840
Is this what you hope for?

1160
00:40:43,920 --> 00:40:45,520
Is this the kind of flourish you want?

1161
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:47,840
We can't sit and wait for that to come, Shizhi.

1162
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:49,440
We have to fight for it.

1163
00:40:49,840 --> 00:40:50,560
There's no making without breaking

1164
00:40:51,040 --> 00:40:53,280
China now needs warriors and fighters.

1165
