Why do we Chinese can do nothing but just watch.

1166
00:40:55,440 --> 00:40:56,880
Watch the Paris Peace Treaty get signed.

1167
00:40:57,120 --> 00:40:59,440
Why should we just watch the loss of Qingdao happening.

1168
00:40:59,680 --> 00:41:00,800
Giving it away to the Japanese without even arguing?

1169
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:02,560
Are we Chinese farm animals?

1170
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:04,800
Shall we just wait for the knives to fall?

1171
00:41:05,040 --> 00:41:05,600
Certainly not

1172
00:41:05,680 --> 00:41:07,920
Shall we just get slaughtered like farm animal?

1173
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:08,960
Certainly not

1174
00:41:09,440 --> 00:41:11,040
I'm not advocating not to fight

1175
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:12,960
I mean, we can't act foolhardy.

1176
00:41:13,200 --> 00:41:14,400
Our power is limited. 

1177
00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:16,400
We should know how to stay away from the mess

1178
